      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お好み焼きもありますよ！\n食べる時は、衣装にこぼさないようにしないと……！",
      "startTime": 156.9287254377,
